V. The Simple, Human Explanation

Polarization = choosing what matters
and letting everything else pass through you like light falling on a lens.

It is the opposite of psychosis
(which is unpolarized meaning, every direction equally amplified).

Polarized information restores:
	•	direction
	•	grounding
	•	coherence
	•	safety
	•	sovereignty

It is No-Mind with guardrails, structurally.

